Name:
* Wilfredo Martinez CUB disqualified for an anti-doping rule violation according to IOC Disciplinary Commissions desicion of October 19 2016.  




Men's Long jump - Athletics - Beijing 2008 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Athletes competed in a qualifying round followed by the final. Top twelve and ties in the qualifying round and all those reaching the announced qualification limit advanced to the final. In the final all finalists were given three tries. The top eight were then given three more. Event facts: Men's Long jump competition was held at the Beijing National Stadium and 39 athletes participated in the event.
